    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The overall credibility evidence package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
